title: Hello.
text: I’m a journalism student at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln graduating in December 2023. I’m passionate about local reporting on the environment, history and policy, and my favorite projects involve all three. I’m a native of northern Minnesota, and I plan to settle somewhere in the northern part of the country and tell the stories of my new community. ​In my spare time, I enjoy reading, hiking and gardening.
